                                <td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">A long time ago charms were changed so that you couldn't recharm without a break.  Undoing this change with the OOW charms, as well as making them a fixed duration could balance the risk to fit the reward of those spells.
<br />

<br />
So for OOW:
<br />
Let a fresh charm overwrite an old one
<br />
Fix the duration so its not random</span><span class="postbody"></span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
