                        <tr>
                                <td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">I am a big proponent of "something needs to be done".
<br />

<br />
That being said, this, IMO, isn't it.
<br />

<br />
If Charm overwrote itself, there is no challenge, we would essentially be getting a permapet.
<br />

<br />
If all Charm lasted max duration, I have wasted my time maxing my cha and spent needless AAXp for TD3.
<br />

<br />
If Charming were easy, everyone would do it, all the time.  This is not my idea of game balancing.   This solution would just be breaking our class even more than it already is.  Just my 2cp though
<br />

<br />
Peace</span><span class="postbody"></span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
