                                <td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">Leaving dps as it is - this still isn't balanced.
<br />

<br />
I can generate 45 dps from lev 62 animation (buffed only with SoV), and another 100+ chain nuking Insanity and Dementing Visions.  That is with no risk.
<br />

<br />
