                                <td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">Last night I got to use charm in a group for CC purposes...
<br />

<br />
It had a dot on it, and the MT pulled a named and an add while a dotted mob was still in camp (don't ask why.....I have no clue... but I don't mind, since it keeps me awake) .  At any rate, the point is... this is my ideal situation for charm: to use it when a mob can't be mezzed but still needs to be controlled...
<br />

<br />
Now it was pretty exciting because charm broke halfway through the fight, I got summoned, and the add showed up at the same time.</span><span class="postbody"><br />_________________<br /><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=406237" target="_blank" class="postlink">Baalazai</a>
